title: Hawkwind SPACE RITUAL Brixton sundown 30-12-72 Complete audience
description:
This is the Brixton show that was recorded for the Space ritual album, which was made up of this and the Liverpool stadium gig.

It is an audience recording of the complete show and although it is a bit rough it is nice to hear the show as it was, without overdubs.

Ive rated it at 7/10
